[h1]Spawn Point Tool[/h1]

Create personal respawn points anywhere you can reach with the Toolgun. Place one point as a checkpoint, or place several and respawn at a random saved point.

[h2]Features[/h2]
[list]
[*]Personal respawn points for each player
[*]Multiple saved points per map
[*]Saved facing direction
[*]Optional persistence across sessions
[*]Placement preview and visible markers
[*]Optional danger and blocked-spot checks
[*]Configurable marker sharing
[*]Player and admin toggles
[/list]

[h2]Controls[/h2]
[list]
[*]Left-click: add a respawn point
[*]Right-click: remove the aimed respawn point
[*]Reload: clear your respawn points on the current map
[/list]

Find it in the Toolgun menu under [b]Spawn Point Tool[/b].

